Items.mt: The main ingredients are white radish, sea cucumber, squid and chicken. The finished product is a white, jade-like, eye-catching peony flower floating on top of the noodles in the soup, and the dish is fragrant and fresh. Don't say you've been to Luoyang if you haven't eaten it.
